      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Cells are clustered using the Louvain algorithm.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper uses Louvain clustering algorithm, not Leiden. Both are community detection algorithms, but the card specifies 'leiden' which is not mentioned in the paper. The paper demonstrates clustering output but with a different algorithm.",
