      "asbval:note": "Paper demonstrates marker gene ranking and identification per cluster, but does not explicitly specify the output format (DataFrame), the specific statistical columns (log fold-change, adjusted p-values), or leiden clustering. The example shows marker gene identification but not the full output structure claimed.",
