      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms Scanpy has preprocessing functions, but does not mention Dask-backed AnnData support. Paper describes HDF5-backed mode instead: 'This allows operating on an ANNDATA object without fully loading it into memory\u2014the functionality is offered via ANNDATA's backed mode as opposed to its memory mode.'",
